        <h3 id="bitcoinMining">Bitcoin Mining</h3>

        <strong> What is Bitcoin mining? </strong>
        <p>
            Bitcoin is a virtual currency that can be traded anomunously online for products and services. Bitcoins are
            'mined' by installing a program on a user's Pc that performs complex calculations. Users are rewarded with
            bitcoins in exchange for their processing power.
        </p>

        <strong> How does a botmaster exploit bitcoin mining?</strong>

        <p>
            The botmaster has the capability to install the bitcoin software on the PC of one of its bots, allowing the
            botmaster to harness the processing power of that computer to mine coins which can then be sold in exchange
            for real currency.
        </p>
